{"id":362724,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/73/407378.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"靠谱人生茶话会","groupHref":"/group/boring","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/03/364.jpg","message":"早上刷MAD，看见弹幕五颜六色且朗朗上口的诗歌，尝试着读出声，发现竟然如此的行。此生无悔二次元，来世还做B站人。<br>此贴总结一下，经典二次元，每句话对应的“动漫”希望后人能够给后人的后人科普。<br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">没有未来的未来，不是我想要的未来</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">时间流逝，愿你有一天能与重要的人重逢</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">天若有情天亦老，我为艾拉续亿秒</span></span><br><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-style:italic\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">如果真爱有颜色，那一定是蓝色</span></span></span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">未闻花名，但识花香。再见花时，泪已千行</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">当黑白之剑交叉之时，这一刻就许下心愿。永远守护你，彼此守护着对方。</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">纵使我身形俱灭，也定将恶鬼斩杀！</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">为王的诞生献上血与泪编辑的荆棘王冠</span></span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">折木弄花千蝶反田，蔷薇穹下旷世恋语！</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">这一切都是命运石之门的选择！</span></span><br><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">赤色月下，妖刀村雨。赤红之瞳，斩断黑暗。</span></span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">你发梢流淌的火焰，是我永生沉沦的爱恋！</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">静待紫藤花凋谢，直至蝴蝶成眠！</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">樱花树下宠物女，来世定缘樱花庄。</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">比起晴天，我跟需要阳菜。</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">音无结下弦之日，悦动天使之心。立于浮华之上，奏响天籁之音。</span></span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">轻音，永不毕业！</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">我喜欢了你十年，却用一整个四月。编织了一个不爱你的谎言。</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">你指尖跳动的电光，是我此生不变的信仰，唯我超电磁炮永世长存！</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">时光流转恨无尽，崎路澪澪梦无期。狂妄不羁掩孤寂，三溯轮回为真情。</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">花无凋谢之日，意无传达之期，爱情亘古不变，紫罗兰永世长存</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">吾王剑锋所指，吾等心之所向！</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">未来已将日记都写下！</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">一座小镇，一个家族，人生太短，回忆太长，译作经典，写作CL，读写人生。</span></span></span><br>希望大家朗诵全文，并且背诵，楼主先去吸会氧。<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"> ","time":"2021-5-5 09:19","title":"非二次元勿入","userId":"harukizzp","userName":"加藤🌕骑士","userSign":"(没有素质的电力工人)"}